<collectingCountry box="[1200,1267,1857,1883]" name="Brazil" pageId="12" pageNumber="243">Brasil</collectingCountry>
Jundiahy 1899 Schrottky [printed] 17.II- [handwritten in red]\ [?] [handwritten in red]\ 
